fields.description:
I have created a policy which limits the number of instances which can be run within an availability zone (the resource).  It has no effect.

{code}
AVAILABILITYZONE	cluster01	192.168.62.5 arn:euca:eucalyptus:cluster01:cluster:cc-01/
{code}

This quota is attached to the account:

{code}
{
 "Statement":[{
   "Effect":"Limit",
   "Action":"ec2:RunInstances",
   "Resource":"arn:aws:ec2:::availabilityzone/cluster01",
   "Condition":{
     "NumericLessThanEquals":{
       "ec2:quota-vminstancenumber":"2"
     }
   }
 }]
}
{code}

Also tried this syntax:

Note - either one is accepted by the policy parser.

{code}
{
 "Statement":[{
   "Effect":"Limit",
   "Action":"ec2:RunInstances",
   "Resource":["arn:aws:ec2:::availabilityzone/cluster01"],
   "Condition":{
     "NumericLessThanEquals":{
       "ec2:quota-vminstancenumber":"2"
     }
   }
 }]
}
{code}



I try to launch 3 instances as the user within the account:

{code}
lester@dreadnought:~/.euca/lwade> euca-run-instances -n 3 -t m1.large -g default -k lwade2 -z cluster01 emi-86903B67
RESERVATION	r-63193DC9	110130730843	default
INSTANCE	i-52F239A3	emi-86903B67	0.0.0.0	0.0.0.0	pending	lwade2	0		m1.large	2012-09-20T11:18:30.966Z	cluster01	eki-EB5C3A47	eri-A6A936DC
INSTANCE	i-9D8041B0	emi-86903B67	0.0.0.0	0.0.0.0	pending	lwade2	1		m1.large	2012-09-20T11:18:30.978Z	cluster01	eki-EB5C3A47	eri-A6A936DC
INSTANCE	i-5C653DAC	emi-86903B67	0.0.0.0	0.0.0.0	pending	lwade2	2		m1.large	2012-09-20T11:18:30.988Z	cluster01	eki-EB5C3A47	eri-A6A936DC
lester@dreadnought:~/.euca/lwade> euca-describe-instances 
RESERVATION	r-63193DC9	110130730843	default
INSTANCE	i-52F239A3	emi-86903B67	192.168.62.64	172.23.109.137	running	lwade2	0		m1.large	2012-09-20T11:18:30.966Z	cluster01	eki-EB5C3A47	eri-A6A936DC
INSTANCE	i-5C653DAC	emi-86903B67	192.168.62.66	172.23.109.154	running	lwade2	2		m1.large	2012-09-20T11:18:30.988Z	cluster01	eki-EB5C3A47	eri-A6A936DC
INSTANCE	i-9D8041B0	emi-86903B67	192.168.62.65	172.23.109.149	running	lwade2	1		m1.large	2012-09-20T11:18:30.978Z	cluster01	eki-EB5C3A47	eri-A6A936DC
{code}

Quota policy appears to have no effect.

